OL,3,CMan threw 'Molotov cocktail' into sex
OL,4,Coffender's flat
OL,6,FA man from who hurled a potentially
OL,7,Flethal "Molotov cocktail" through the
OL,8,Fwindow of a neighbour who was a
OL,9,Fconvicted sex offender has been jailed.
OL,11,FThe fuel-filled bottle thrown by 30-
OL,12,Fyear-old Simon Boothby burst into
OL,13,Fflames in the man's property.
OL,15,FThe victim managed to get his
OL,16,Fgirlfriend and dogs to safety before
OL,17,Fgoing back into the kitchen to try to
OL,18,Ftackle the flames that were three feet
OL,19,Fhigh, Hull Crown Court heard.
