OL,3,CMan threw 'Molotov cocktail' into sex
OL,4,Coffender's flat
OL,6,FStephen Robinson, prosecuting, said
OL,7,Fthat the man lived in an upstairs flat
OL,8,Fand Boothby lived nearby. The man had
OL,9,Fpreviously heard that Boothby was not
OL,10,Fhappy about him living on that street.
OL,12,FHe overheard Boothby tell a neighbour
OL,13,Fthat the man "needs to get out of
OL,14,Fhere".
OL,16,FCCTV had captured the incident and
OL,17,FBoothby was later detained but he told
OL,18,Fpolice: "I haven't been here. I have
OL,19,Fan alibi."
