OL,3,CMan threw 'Molotov cocktail' into sex
OL,4,Coffender's flat
OL,6,FHis home was searched and a torn rag
OL,7,Fwas found in the bathroom that matched
OL,8,Fone found outside that had fallen down
OL,9,Ffrom the broken window.
OL,11,FA screw-top from a bottle was found on
OL,12,Fa sink and it was from the broken one
OL,13,Fused as a "Molotov cocktail" to attack
OL,14,Fthe flat. There was a fuel canister in
OL,15,Fhis hallway cupboard.
OL,17,FDuring police interview, Boothby
OL,18,Fdenied any knowledge of an arson and
OL,19,Fthat he had called the man a
OL,20,Fpaedophile.
