OL,3,CMan threw 'Molotov cocktail' into sex
OL,4,Coffender's flat
OL,6,FMr Robinson said that the man was a
OL,7,Fconvicted sex offender and he had
OL,8,Fsince moved to another address.
OL,10,FThe man said in a statement that he
OL,11,Ffelt frightened all the time, not just
OL,12,Ffor himself but for his girlfriend. He
OL,13,Fwas on edge and could not sleep. He
OL,14,Fhad been frightened to leave his home
OL,15,Fin case he got targeted.
OL,17,FSimon Boothby, 30, of Deerhurst Grove,
OL,18,FBransholme, Hull, admitted arson with
OL,19,Fintent to endanger life on September 5.
