OL,6,FHelen Chapman, mitigating, said that
OL,7,FBoothby remained angry that the man
OL,8,Fhad been placed in a flat near him and
OL,9,Fnear women and children.
OL,11,F"He struggles to contain his emotions
OL,12,Fon that topic," said Miss Chapman
OL,13,Fadding "He does regret his actions and
OL,14,Fhe does appreciate that he could have
OL,15,Ffound himself in far more serious
OL,16,Ftrouble with the police but, also, he
OL,17,Fcould have had two deaths on his
OL,18,Fhands."
