OL,6,F"This was a determined attempt and a
OL,7,Fserious attack and you no doubt picked
OL,8,Fyour time so that you would not be
OL,9,Fdetected and they were not likely to
OL,10,Fbe disturbed or awoken by what was
OL,11,Fgoing on.
OL,13,F"It was sheer good fortune that the
OL,14,Fcomplainant was able to control and
OL,15,Fdouse the fire by water. He spotted a
OL,16,Fglass bottle that was on the floor,
OL,17,Fthat had not been there previously,
OL,18,Fand that the window was broken.
