OL,6,F"That was clearly as a consequence of
OL,7,Fyour lobbing the glass bottle, which
OL,8,Fwas set alight, through the kitchen
OL,9,Fwindow. There was extensive damage to
OL,10,Fthat property.
OL,12,FBoothby, who was already in custody on
OL,13,Fremand, was sentenced to six years in
OL,14,Fprison after being branded a dangerous
OL,15,Foffender. He will be on extended
OL,16,Flicence of three years after his
OL,17,Frelease from prison.
